      <abstract>The Volga Germans of Milliken, Colorado, formed the German Congregational Church in
        1918. The church joined with the United Church of Christ at some point after 1957. The
        church closed in 1977. This collection contains two registers that contain vital membership
        records which include baptismal records, marriage records, confirmation records, and Sunday
        school records.</abstract>
